title: Greek Style Veggie Mince and Cheese Roll with Roasted Garlic Yogurt, Zesty Spiced Chips and Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Greek Style Veggie Mince and Cheese Roll is perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
